metadata.title: National Tree MZC-638A Pre-Lit Joy Decoration, 27"
features: Pre-lit with 13 warm White LED lights
Battery operated (3 AA batteries, not included)
Metal wire and linen fabric construction
description: This Christmas decoration consists of three individual letters made of wire frame construction with linen fabric facings. Each facing is trimmed with snow-dusted pine needles and red berries. The letters are lit with a combined total of 13 warm white LED lights that are battery operated. For indoor display only.
